Set Theme "ayu"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 720
Set TypingSpeed 80ms
Set Margin 20

Type "cd D:\\Github_Workstation\\GitProjects\\Lenv"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "lenv --help"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "lenv release-notes --version v1.0.0"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "lenv profile list"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "lenv runtime status"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "lenv provenance"
Enter
Sleep 2s
